<div id="pf4" class="pf w2 hd" data-page-no="4"><div class="pc pc4 w2 hd"><div class="t m79 xa he y5f ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Meet the Principal Contributor of </div><div class="t m7a x13 he y60 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This Quarter&apos;s Lessons </div><div class="t m7b x20 hf y61 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Rosalie Haffner Lee trains and supervises Bible instructors in the Carolina </div><div class="t m2f x1d hf y62 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Conference. Working as a Bible instructor and a pastor&apos;s wife has been the focus </div><div class="t m7c x1d hf y63 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of her career. </div><div class="t m7d x20 hf y64 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mrs. Lee received her Bachelor of Arts degree from Union College, and </div><div class="t m7e x1d hf y65 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">served as Bible instructor in California, Nebraska, and Michigan. She was an in-</div><div class="t m7f x1d hf y66 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">structor for the North American Division Evangelism Institute in Illinois before </div><div class="t m80 x1d hf y67 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accepting the position in the Carolina Conference. </div><div class="t m81 x20 hf y68 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mrs. Lee has written a previous set of Sabbath School lessons, </div><div class="t m82 x21 h10 y69 ff8 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Songs of Ex-</div><div class="t m83 x1d h10 y6a ff8 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perience, </div><div class="t m84 x22 hf y6b ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on the Psalms, and authored a book entitled </div><div class="t m85 x23 h10 y6c ff8 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Let Me Tell You About My </div><div class="t m86 x12 h10 y6d ff8 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God. </div><div class="t m87 x2 hf y6e ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In addition she has written for several Adventist publications. </div><div class="t m88 x20 hf y6f ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Cooking, writing, and bird-watching occupy Mrs. Lee&apos;s leisure moments. Her </div><div class="t m89 x1d hf y70 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">husband, Kenneth, is a retired pastor. </div><div class="t m8a x11 h11 y71 ff5 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Check at your local Adventist Book Center </div><div class="t m8b x11 h11 y72 ff5 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the companion book to the Sabbath </div><div class="t m8c x11 h11 y73 ff5 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">School Lessons. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
